file_content.text: Taking this factory will change everything. Good luck.
Welcome to Darvannis. Try not to die.
Let's see what you can do.
Heard you're up against a whole battalion this time. Don't forget to grab a few trophies.
It works. A little too well, to be honest. Pushes a lot harder when I run, throws me off balance. Still getting used to it.
You'll get there. Bet you'll be stomping droid domes with it by the end of the week. Think they'll appreciate the irony?
